BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ centimeter} = 10 \text{ millimeters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$cm1] \text{ centimeters} = ``] [__________]{$mm1} [`` \text{ millimeters} ``]

a. [`` [$mm2] \text{ millimeters} = ``] [__________]{$cm2} [`` \text{ centimeters} ``]

END_PGML


